page_title: 'Using your data with Azure OpenAI Service'
page_description: Use this article to learn about using your data for better text generation in Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: Get startedTo get started, connect your data source using Azure OpenAI Studio and start asking questions and chatting on your data.> [!NOTE]> To get started, you need to already have been approved for Azure OpenAI access and have an Azure OpenAI Service resource deployed in a supported region with either the gpt-35-turbo or the gpt-4 models.
